<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NURUL HIDAYAH | 3D Cyber Deep Blue Edition</title>
    
    <!-- IBM Plex Sans & Orbitron Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        /* CSS INTERNAL UNTUK EFEK 3D & ANIMASI KHUSUS */
        :root {
            --electric-blue: #00d4ff;
            --deep-ibm: #0f62fe;
            --dark-core: #001a66;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001a66 0%, #0033cc 50%, #00d4ff 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            perspective: 1000px; /* Base for 3D Effects */
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Glitch & Cyber Effect untuk Nama */
        .cyber-name {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--electric-blue), 0 0 20px var(--electric-blue);
            animation: float3D 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float3D {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateZ(0) rotateX(0); }
            50% { transform: translateZ(50px) rotateX(5deg); }
        }

        /* 3D Card Effect */
        .tilt-card {
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .tilt-card:hover {
            transform: rotateY(15deg) rotateX(10deg) translateZ(20px);
            box-shadow: -20px 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        /* Staff Bulat Floating */
        .staff-avatar {
            width: 160px; height: 160px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid #fff;
            background: var(--dark-core);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.6);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            transition: 0.5s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .staff-avatar:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
            border-color: var(--electric-blue);
        }

        /* Scanner Laser Line */
        .scanner-line {
            position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 3px;
            background: var(--electric-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--electric-blue);
            animation: scan3D 4s infinite linear;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        @keyframes scan3D {
            0% { top: 0; opacity: 0; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
            100% { top: 100%; opacity: 0; }
        }

        .glass-panel-3d {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="particles-js" style="position: fixed; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: -1;"></div>

    <div class="main-wrapper" style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 20px;">
        
        <!-- HEADER SECTION -->
        <header style="margin-bottom: 100px;">
            <h1 class="cyber-name" data-aos="zoom-in">NURUL HIDAYAH</h1>
            <div style="text-align: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 5px; opacity: 0.8;">
                <span style="border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;">QUANTUM EDUCATION INTERFACE</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- 15 BINGKAI SANGAT BESAR (DOKUMENTASI UTAMA) -->
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; margin-bottom: 40px; border-left: 10px solid #fff; padding-left: 20px;" data-aos="fade-right">
            // MAIN ARCHIVE: 15_CORE_UNITS
        </h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 120px;">
            <% for(let i=1; i<=15; i++) { %>
                <div class="tilt-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="<%= i * 50 %>">
                    <div style="border: 4px solid #fff; background: #000; padding: 15px; position: relative;">
                        <div class="scanner-line"></div>
                        <div style="height: 380px; background: var(--dark-core); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: var(--electric-blue);">
                            LARGE_DOCK_<%= i %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- 25 BINGKAI SEDANG (SECONDARY ARCHIVE) -->
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; margin-bottom: 40px; border-left: 10px solid var(--electric-blue); padding-left: 20px;" data-aos="fade-right">
            // SUB ARCHIVE: 25_DATA_POINTS
        </h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 120px;">
            <% for(let j=1; j<=25; j++) { %>
                <div class="tilt-card" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <div style="border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); padding: 5px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                        <div style="height: 180px; background: #0033cc; border: 1px dashed #fff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.5;">
                            MED_ARC_<%= j %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- 8 BINGKAI STAFF BULAT (PENGELOLA) -->
        <h2 style="text-align: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; margin-bottom: 60px;">BOARD OF DIRECTORS</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 50px; margin-bottom: 120px;">
            <% 
            const staff = [
                {n: 'IMAT JUNAEDAH, S.Pd.I', r: 'Kepala Sekolah'},
                {n: 'ATANG ABDURAHMAN', r: 'Manager'},
                {n: 'MASPUPAH, S.Pd', r: 'Sekertaris'},
                {n: 'APIPULLOH ASHIDIQ, S.T.I', r: 'Operator'},
                {n: 'SRI INDAH', r: 'Guru'},
                {n: 'NABILA FAUZIAH', r: 'Guru'},
                {n: 'SALWA NOVIYANTI', r: 'Guru'},
                {n: 'JAJANG NURJAMAN', r: 'Bendahara'}
            ];
            %>
            <% staff.forEach((s) => { %>
                <div style="text-align: center;" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <div class="staff-avatar" style="margin: 0 auto 20px;">
                        <span style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--electric-blue);">IMG_FILE</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans'; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem;"><%= s.n %></div>
                    <div style="color: var(--electric-blue); font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px;"><%= s.r %></div>
                </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>

        <!-- VISI MISI KB & MI (SOLID IBM GLASS) -->
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; margin-bottom: 120px;">
            <div class="glass-panel-3d tilt-card" data-aos="fade-right">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: var(--electric-blue); border-bottom: 2px solid #fff; padding-bottom: 10px;">KB NURUL HIDAYAH</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300;">
                    "Membentuk generasi Rabbani yang unggul, berakhlak mulia, dan adaptif terhadap perkembangan teknologi sejak usia dini."
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">Menyelenggarakan pendidikan holistik yang mengintegrasikan nilai-nilai Tauhid dengan literasi digital dasar.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel-3d tilt-card" data-aos="fade-left">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: #fff; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--electric-blue); padding-bottom: 10px;">MI NURUL HIDAYAH</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                    Kurikulum Keislaman: Tarbiyah, Ta'lim, dan Ta'dib sebagai dasar pengajaran dan pembentukan adab/akhlak mulia.
                </p>
                <ul style="color: var(--electric-blue); padding-left: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    <li>Madrasah Diniyah Takmiliyah</li>
                    <li>Penguasaan Ulumuddin Mendalam</li>
                    <li>Islamic Environment Rahmatan lil 'Alamiin</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SEJARAH PENDIRI (PALING BAWAH - SOLID BLUE) -->
        <section class="glass-panel-3d" style="background: #fff; color: #001a66;" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 60px;">SEJARAH PENDIRIAN</h2>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 60px; align-items: center;">
                <div class="tilt-card" style="width: 400px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                    <div style="border: 15px solid #001a66; padding: 10px; background: #000;">
                        <div style="height: 450px; background: #001a66; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-family: 'Orbitron';">FOUNDER_PHOTO</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 900; font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 1.2rem;">MUSTOFA, MUI</div>
                </div>
                <div style="flex: 1; font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans'; line-height: 2; font-size: 1.2rem; text-align: justify;">
                    <p>"Ponpes Nurul Hidayah didirikan dengan tekad mulia: memberikan akses pendidikan berkualitas yang menyinergikan kecerdasan intelektual dan kedalaman spiritual. Berawal dari visi <strong>KH. MUSTOFA</strong>, tokoh ulama Indonesia yang peduli terhadap masa depan generasi muda."</p>
                    <p>"Sekolah ini tumbuh dari langkah-langkah kecil penuh perjuangan. Melalui komitmen kuat para pendiri dan dedikasi guru, Nurul Hidayah kini terus berkembang menjadi institusi pembentuk karakter."</p>
                    <p>"Beliau percaya bahwa setiap anak adalah amanah, dan sejarah kami adalah perjalanan panjang menjaga amanah tersebut untuk generasi yang lebih baik."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Mandatory Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init({ duration: 1000, once: true });
        particlesJS('particles-js', {
            "particles": {
                "number": { "value": 100 },
                "color": { "value": "#ffffff" },
                "shape": { "type": "circle" },
                "opacity": { "value": 0.5 },
                "size": { "value": 3 },
                "line_linked": { "enable": true, "distance": 150, "color": "#ffffff", "opacity": 0.2, "width": 1 },
                "move": { "enable": true, "speed": 2 }
            }
        });

        // 3D Parallax Mouse Move Effect
        document.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
            const amount = 20;
            const x = (e.clientX / window.innerWidth - 0.5) * amount;
            const y = (e.clientY / window.innerHeight - 0.5) * amount;
            document.querySelectorAll('.tilt-card').forEach(card => {
                card.style.transform = `rotateY(${x}deg) rotateX(${-y}deg)`;
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
